		{
			dependencies: ["32B6A25A9A456DEB"]
			description: [
				"Smaller \"ambient\" animals like these &aButterflies&r are simple creatures. More complex animals can be tamed and claimed."
				""
				"After breeding some additional butterflies, try out this &aChinchilla&r next. It is still small enough to catch by hand, and can be tamed with &9herbivore kibble&r."
				""
				"(You may read in wikis that ZAWA animals need to be fed and watered after being tamed; this is not the case. Your animals will be perfectly happy in their exhibits without your constant attention.)"
			]
