		{
			dependencies: ["73C46B64A89E4627"]
			description: [
				"Now that you have a few creatures to show off, it's time to let in some visitors. Make yourself a &9Zoo Donation Barrel&r and then place it in the center of your new zoo."
				""
				"Throughout the day, &aZoogoers&r will enter your zoo via the barrel, and wander around admiring the animals you have gathered. At the end of the day, they will return to where they came from. If they liked your zoo, they'll leave a donation of &9emeralds&r! The more animal species you add, the larger your donations will be."
				""
				"Naturally, more exotic animals will impress your &aZoogoers&r more. Build more exhibits to earn more money!"
			]
			id: "2AC8599400B467E3"
			rewards: [{
				id: "32174869731B79DF"
				type: "xp_levels"
				xp_levels: 3
			}]
			tasks: [{
				id: "35762F15E3FBDFA0"
				item: "zoogoer:zoo_donation_barrel_block"
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Time for Customers!"
			x: -7.0d
			y: 1.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2AC8599400B467E3"]
			description: [
				"Once you have built up some funds, you can construct other kinds of donation barrels, to invite in specialist guests. These guests prefer to see specific kinds of animals. For example, &aBird Watchers&r are twice as interested in any birds you will show them, and only half as interested as a normal &aZoogoer&r in other kinds of animals. If they see a lot of animals they like, they may even leave various items as tips."
				""
				"As you build out specialized areas of your zoo, make sure to place the right kind of &9donation barrel&r near the right exhibits."
			]
			id: "360F892F0B5BD1BF"
